# ResolveDesk Root GitIgnore

# 1. Dependency Directories
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# 2. Environment Variables & Secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.*env
**/.*env.*

# 3. Build & Output Directories
dist/
build/
.next/
out/

# 4. Logs and Diagnostic Files
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

# 5. Operating System Junk
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# 6. IDEs and Editors
.idea/
.vscode/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.swp

# 7. Prisma Specifics
# We want to commit schema.prisma and prisma.config.ts, 
# but if you ever use SQLite for local quick testing, ignore the DB file.
*.db
*.db-journal